title: Harry Potter Audiobooks 1-7 Narrated by Stephen Fry
description:
All of the Harry Poter audio books, narrated by Stephen Fry, formatted for iTunes with correct metadata (including cover images and chapter markers). M4B files, books 5-7 are split into 2 parts to preserve sound quality in a small file size.

Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone
Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets
Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban
Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire
Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix
Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix Part 2
Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince
Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince Part 2
Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows
Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows Part 2

Enjoy :)
